-I heard such words all the time.
Just give it up. There will only be more gray hair on my head if I teach you sojutsu. "
"If you want to learn something, then there are no barriers in front of you, but your productivity is too lame."
Hey, let's pick the herbs, herbs. Why are you trying to learn only the art of the sword? "
"Just live like everyone else."

e5148679-29de-4fff-b1a1-c77c44c41d5a.title: Crest of the Stars
descriptionParagraphs: 2012 manga running in Comic Meteor.

Crest of the Stars follow Jinto Lynn, a young count whose world is taken over by the space-dwelling race of the Abh. When Jinto was a young boy, his father, Rock Lynn, under threat of invasion, handed over their world, Martine, to the Abh in exchange for a position within Abh society. Young Jinto is sent off to school to learn the ways of Abh nobility and the story of Crest of the Stars picks up as he meets the young Abh princess, Lafiel as they are about to travel to military school for Jinto's further training.

However, in the midst of their travels, Lafiel and Jinto (along with the Abh ship Gothlauth, a.k.a. Gosroth) find themselves at the very beginnings of a war between the Abh Empire and the Four Nations Alliance of humankindan anti-Abh alliance of the democratic nations of the United Mankind, the Federation of Hania, the Republic of Greater Alcont, and the People's Sovereign Union of Planets.

cd5d08b9-ca54-49c4-853d-b167089c19a9.title: The Snail in My House
alternateTitles: The Story of My Snail and I
descriptionParagraphs: The condition for the fresh water snail to become a human being is to win the love of its housemate? Seungha, someone from ordinary single-member household, once came across with a feisty snail called 'Nokjo'. A cool-sweet healing living together romance of the top-level housekeeping neat freak snail and Seungha, the weary loner in her hectic routine.

787e365d-7254-4509-820a-b63cc44331a9.title: The Story of Hua Yan
descriptionParagraphs: The almighty crowned prince insists on marrying this young Overgrown Apricot lady from the tainted Hua family. When the news broke out in the capital, many hearts were broken but what?! This wicked woman doesnt even want to be the crowned princess because she wants to drink and run away with another man?!
Lady Hua: I am a tough woman. Im definitely not suited for you!
Crowned Prince: Then Ill make sure that in this world, you can only pick me.

bb1ba906-fdad-4791-8917-86e76912b6ce.title: Kobatotei Ibun
alternateTitles: The Strange Story of the Kobato Residence
descriptionParagraphs: Something happened to Kobato when he was young, something he can't explain. Since then he's been able to see things that normal people can't see. These are the touching tales of his and others' experiences with the unknown.

7a9ea386-c960-4752-9035-7c652c1b97af.title: Shinohayu - The Dawn of Age
alternateTitles: Side Story of - Saki - Shinohayu the Dawn of Age
descriptionParagraphs: A prequel to the Saki series, focusing on Shino Shiratsuki, a young girl with an affinity for the 1-sou who is seeking out her missing mother. Future professional mahjong players like Hayari Mizuhara, Harue Akado and others are also featured.

b33ca79b-a974-4fa1-a327-97fd6c029a76.title: The Story of How I Found My Cat
alternateTitles: The Story That I Picked Up A Cat
descriptionParagraphs: One rainy day, Igai picked up a one eyed, three-legged cat. The problem is... he's not sure it's actually a cat.

3f39cec9-d5d0-4c61-b8f9-0534c437d376.title: Teihen Ryoushu no Kanchigai Eiyuutan
alternateTitles: The Story of Lord, Devasted Manor who Grows by Misunderstanding
descriptionParagraphs: Baibalon, a territory considered the worst in the country. A place where those who have no home left flee to, filled with criminals, heretics, sick people and demihumans.

Taking over the family as the next Lord, the young Rize Baibalon will try his best to stay alive in this god-forsaken place, not worrying if what he does to achieve that goal is going against the very founding doctrine of the country.
With little common sense and recovery magic, can he accomplish his peace? Or will the misunderstandings continue to pile up and will he be branded as a Rebel?

ae3e8911-7c27-489c-8cf2-736a3924558c.title: Mismarca Koukoku Monogatari
descriptionParagraphs: Mahiro is the prince of Mismarca Kingdom, he won't study nor learn sword skills, he is a lazy prince who only plays until late night. His Imperial Bodyguard Pariel would always scold him for his behaviour. And towards that Mismarca Kingdom, an elite squad from the Demonic Kingdom Granmarsenal is approaching. The Leader of the squad is Lunas, a warrior princess, the third Princess of Granmarsenal. All of Mismarca's vassals voiced their will of fight and bring an all-out war, though there is one man said cowardly "Why don't we have a talk with them?". What kind of fate awaits Mismarca Kingdom and its useless Prince, Mahiro?
Adaptation of the light novel series of the same name written by Tomaki Hayashi with illustrations by Tomozo.

2ea089e6-750d-4856-9097-96eda5542e21.title: Yuwakashi Yuusha no Fukushuutan
alternateTitles: The Tale of the Teapot Hero's Revenge
The Tale of the Teapot Hero's Revenge ~Although a Hero Was Only Capable of Boiling Water, That Was Enough to Kill All of Those Who Stole Everything from Her~
descriptionParagraphs: A Hero is someone chosen by God to receive a supernatural 'gift'. A unique existence, only one Hero can exist at a time, with a new one being chosen upon the former's death.
This generation's Hero is an ordinary villager girl named Kyrie whose gift is merely being able to boil water.

When her family and friends are slaughtered, Kyrie is backed into a corner and learns the true value of that boiling hot power, and how well it could be used to fan the flames of revenge that burned inside of her.

e9c733e8-4d06-4618-b604-577281f857ee.title: Hoshi no Koimonogatari
alternateTitles: Love Stories of the 12 Signs of the Zodiac
descriptionParagraphs: Originally published in the April 2015 issue of Comic Spica, this is a series of astrology-themed one-shots created by different mangaka and collected in an anthology.
Sennen no Kodoku (Millennium Loneliness) by FUJIWARA Kaoru
A man devotes himself to pray in church.
Himitsu (Secret) by SHIMURA Takako
Magazine editor Nanase sees a poplar tree on the go. That fateful encounter, evokes the memory of a certain secret
Nandemonai Kinou no Hanashi (My Unexceptional Yesterday) by Itoi Nozo
A woman has a seemingly unremarkable story about a chance meeting.

fdb14889-59ef-48dd-a883-7558f04c2060.title: Ryoumin 0-nin Start no Henkyou Ryoushusama
alternateTitles: The Population of the Frontier Owner Starts With 0. "Dias the Blue" and a Blue-Horned Girl.
descriptionParagraphs: Dias fulfilled his parents' will to help others, and kept fighting on the battlefield to that end. Now known as the "Savior Hero" from his long wartime career, he was rewarded with a vast territory from the king. After having met the horned Kijin () girl Aruna who lives there, he begins his new slow life as a lord, seeking to thrive in spite of increasingly realizing that he was rewarded with the short end of the stick.
- Japanese Light Novel:

56efe33b-09f6-4e56-a0c0-780d815ed043.title: Hoshi no Kirby! - Moretsu Pupupu Awa
alternateTitles: Kirby of the Stars! Raging Pupupu Hour!
descriptionParagraphs: In the first volume, Kirby gets involved with the Squeak Squad and causes a ruckus in the violently peaceful Pupupu Land, and from the middle of the second volume onward, King Dedede and the inhabitants of Pupupu Land enjoy various events and carry out funny incidents.

eb26ab13-148d-48e1-bff4-dcf59c4986a0.title: Isekai Maou to Shoukan Shoujo no Dorei Majutsu
alternateTitles: How NOT to Summon a Demon Lord
The King of Darkness Another World Story ~ Slave Magic
The King of Darkness Another World Story: Slave Magic
The Other World Demon King and the Summoning Girls Slave Magic
descriptionParagraphs: When it comes to the fantasy MMORPG Cross Reverie, none can match the power of the Demon King Diablo.

Possessing the game's rarest artifacts and an unrivaled player level, he overpowers all foolish enough to confront him. But despite his fearsome reputation, Diablo's true identity is Takuma Sakamoto, a shut-in gamer devoid of any social skills.

Defeating hopeless challengers day by day, Takuma cares about nothing else but his virtual lifethat is, until a summoning spell suddenly transports him to another world where he has Diablo's appearance!
In this new world resembling his favorite game, Takuma is greeted by the two girls who summoned him: Rem Galeu, a petite Pantherian adventurer, and Shera L. Greenwood, a busty Elf summoner.

They perform an Enslavement Ritual in an attempt to subjugate him, but the spell backfires and causes them to become his slaves instead. With the situation now becoming more awkward than ever, Takuma decides to accompany the girls in finding a way to unbind their contract while learning to adapt to his new existence as the menacing Demon King.

34d4ed85-1fe3-4f4f-914d-4bde5217a0f5.title: A Story About a Very Lonely Female President Who Instantly Falls for a Lesbian Prostitute
alternateTitles: A Story About a Very Lonely Female CEO Who Falls for a Lesbian Prostitute in Seconds
The Story of a Lonely Female President Who Instantly Falls for a Female Lesbian Worker
descriptionParagraphs: She has money, status, and fame. Even though she has everything, she can't compensate for her loneliness. How can she become satisfied? The destination that such a female president headed for was... A lesbian brothel?? Furthermore, she ended up instantly falling in love?!

e7c88847-9a61-4856-94db-fefae51a1d28.title: The Former Structural Analyst's Otherworldly Adventure Story
alternateTitles: Adventures of a Former Structural Analyst
The Former Structural Researcher's Otherworldly Adventure Story
The Former Structural Researcher's Story of Otherworldly Adventure
descriptionParagraphs: Kaoru Mochimizu, a 30-year-old female research scientist who studied the three-dimensional structure of everything. However, one day, she died in an earthquake and met a goddess. Having covered for her kouhai during the earthquake, she was allowed to reincarnate in another world with two skils. Kaoru Mochimizu is now Charlotte Elbaran, the eldest daughter of a duke in the Kingdom of Elida, on Planet Garland. With memories of her past life, and taking advantage of the skills "Structural Analysis" and "Structural Editing," she will live a good life.

ad59c8bb-e645-41d2-bc16-65b1b94cafd6.title: Tenohira Kaitaku Mura de Isekai Kenkokuki: Fueteku Yome-tachi to Nonbiri Mujintou Life
alternateTitles: Country Building Story in Another World with the Pioneering Village in His Palm ~Easy Life on the Uninhabited Island with His Ever Increasing Wives~
Foundation of a State in Another World With a Hand-Built Colony Village ~Carefree Life on an Uninhabitated Island With an Increasing Number of Brides~
With Single Palm Founding a Pioneering Village a in Another World - Live With The Married Girls in Uninhabited Island Life ~
descriptionParagraphs: Kai, a sickly kid, wished for a lively normal life on his deathbed when he was suddenly reincarnated into another world. Not only the boys wishes were fulfilled, he was also gifted an ability to be a god of his own little world at the back of his palm. Yet such bliss did not last long

Kai was abruptly separated from his loving adopted family and banished into an uninhabited island teeming with dangerous creatures. Using his ingenious wit and a help from a mysterious horned girl, Kai managed to survive and establish a small foothold with his army of cute stubby helpers.
Watch as Kai tries to further tame this wilderness, building up his sanctuary and harem. Easy living!

c8e83aab-43e8-425c-bd55-e7fa7fd666f7.title: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken Ibun: Makoku Gurashi no Trinity
alternateTitles: That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime Another Story: Trinity of the Magic Kingdom
That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime: Trinity in Tempest
That Time I Was Reincarnated As A Slime Strange Report: Tempest Life of Trinity
descriptionParagraphs: Against the odds, the little slime Rimiru has established his magical kingdom for all monsters, called Tempest, and its thriving. But three visitors, Phos the fox girl, Stella the dragon girl, and Frey the winged girl, come to pay Tempest a visit, theyre stunned at just how quickly its developed. Dont miss this new story in the world of Slime
***Warning:***
Potential Spoilers for the main manga.

8eaaec7d-7aa7-490e-8d52-5a3d0a28e78b.title: A Story About a Man and a Woman and When They Sleep Together, Money Appears Out of Nowhere
alternateTitles: Ichaicha suruto okane ga wai chau danjo no hanashi
descriptionParagraphs: Money will spring?! A pure comedy open love comedy!

A boy with a blunt but gentle heart, Aki, and a warm girl, Haru. When two poor college students flirt, they get money for some reason? A comedy that aims to be a flirt while pretending to be "for money" while keeping their love for each other!
*Chapter numbering is based on

677fb60b-2deb-46db-9ece-704f6144faf0.title: The Story Between a Dumb Prefect and a High School Girl with an Inappropriate Skirt Length
alternateTitles: Story of the Useless Prefect and the High School Girl with an Inappropriate Skirt Length
descriptionParagraphs: Sakuradaimon is the school's prefect. A prefect is a student who is authorized to enforce discipline. As a prefect, he's supposed to be a role model to other students, but unfortunately he's not perfect. Kohinata is one of the people who Sakuradaimon has tried to discipline into wearing appropriate school attire, but she has thus far been disobedient.
And so this is a story of the two interacting with one another.
Author's twitter:

e6fe82a8-02c8-4d87-adda-1b92db67b377.title: Weekly Boys' Romance
alternateTitles: The weekly love story of young men
descriptionParagraphs: Five boys, living under the same roof, yet indifferent to one another, are given an ultimatum: "No girl problems, or you're out". With each of them harboring their own unconventional romance, can they succeed in protecting their clumsy, innocent love and rebuild their friendship?
A love/hate drama filled story about 5 highschoolers who live in the same house.

bf4a285b-636d-4760-9a90-e538514bf024.title: Hoshi no Kirby - Pupupu Hero
alternateTitles: Kirby of the Stars - Pupupu Hero
descriptionParagraphs: An adaptation of the Kirby games, particularly following Super Star Ultra, Epic Yarn, and Return to Dreamland. Follows the adventures of Kirby and Chilly, along with other characters such as King Dedede, Meta Knight, and Magolor.
Take note that it reads left-to-right.

5705813a-91fc-4f5a-af0d-b4f2c2a194f4.title: The Story of a Guy Who Fell in Love with His Friends Sister
descriptionParagraphs: Arisawa Haruto, falls in love with his friend's sister at the beginning of his second year of middle school. How will this relationship evolve, will he manage to overcome the age difference?

a5fe1bd9-3e02-40f9-be4f-8852b69cabf7.title: Fuyu Fenrir no Itoshigo to Natta Watashi ga, Zetsubou kara Iyasareteiku Hanashi
alternateTitles: I Became the Beloved Child of Winter Fenrir: A Story of Being Healed From Despair
The Story About How I Became the Daughter of Winter Fenrir, Healing From Despair
descriptionParagraphs: "When I got fired from my job, I went to a different world"

Fujioka Noelle is a hard worker for a black company, but her efforts go unrewarded when she is handed a notice of dismissal one day. Frustrated and sinking into despair, she was suddenly transported to another world

In front of the bewildered Noelle appeared Fenrir, the large, silvery-white wolf. Taking a liking to her, they took her into their care as their 'beloved daughter.' Before long, in the midst of her healing, she became caught up in events that will change the world

bda551f4-1a41-42cb-9260-3bbdbe47ae72.title: Naka no Warui Iinazuke no Hanashi
alternateTitles: The Story of an Engaged Couple That Doesn't Get Along
descriptionParagraphs: "The red string is tangling but binding," or so they say.

Despite being betrothed by their parents, these two do NOT get along. They curse one another whenever they're face to face, but their true feelings? Completely the opposite. The two, who just can't be honest, assume that "I bet he/she only cares about himself/herself" - but they might actually love each other?!
Seriously, why can't they just be married? Because they already are? Soon that is!

fbd2ccea-7121-468f-b46f-cd5b3b918bcf.title: Mononobe Koshoten Kaikitan
alternateTitles: Bizarre Records of Mononobe Used Book Store
The Curious Records of the Mononobe Antique Bookshop
descriptionParagraphs: Shoutaro is a man of few words. He manages a used books store called Mononobe Koshoten and has an efficient young boy named Shiro to help out with the work while he reads the day away. But behind this normal and mundane facade Shoutaro has another job: the collection of some rather unpleasant old books
Author's Twitter:

ba210374-7967-4c3e-972d-891a530c992a.title: I Will Be Selfish in a Different World! The Story of a Selfish Saint Candidate
alternateTitles: I Will Be Selfish in a Different World! The Story of a Selfish Saint Candidate
Rikoteki na Seijin Kouho: Toriaezu Isekai de Wagamama Sasetemoraimasu
The Selfish Saint Canidate: I Will Be Selfish in Another World!
descriptionParagraphs: Hatsuko Obata, also known as "Oba-chan," had taken care of her younger brothers on behalf of her busy parents. She can now finally leave hers parents' house to get a job and enjoy her freedom! Or so she thought. Due to a god's mistake, she met her demise. As an apology, she was given a choice between becoming a saint and starting over in a different world, so she chose to reincarnate in order to fulfill her dream of "living freely." With many cheats given to her by an apologetic God, she can now enjoy another world as much as she wants with her different skills and protections!

32179375-989e-47d0-92b9-cb6c893c6e03.title: The Story of My Papa Who Is Always Behind Me
descriptionParagraphs: Author's Twitter: https://twitter.com/k193com

f191f103-5105-4e4c-b708-4862f28b887a.title: The Terrifying Hitman and The Little Girl He Took in (Fan Colored)
alternateTitles: The Story of a Terrifying Hitman and a Little Girl
descriptionParagraphs: A homeless girl is rescued and brought home by a Hitman. He then helps her out and gives her a place to live.

97223152-aefd-4f9b-91c9-39393d8494a0.title: BOX! Kira Ito Tanpenshuu
alternateTitles: BOX! Kira Ito's Short Stories Collection
The Story of a Cat That Has Lived for 100 Years
descriptionParagraphs: A work packed with stories that make you cry, smile, and heal.
A compilation of original short stories, including commercial oneshots and manga previously published on Twitter.
To You at 17th: A mysterious high school girl appeared and sent letters to Mirai
The Story of a Cat That Has Lived for 100 Years : This is a story of a cat that has become immortal, wandering through the course of its lifetime to find happiness.

0621ecc9-c098-4660-ab53-4816a2cadd29.title: Tendou-ke Monogatari
descriptionParagraphs: A girl saves Houjou family's third daughter from drowning herself. The girl takes her place as Houjou Ran who shall become the Tendou family's bride but her deceit is seen through..?

674c0331-a8b8-4ead-8ff9-d78895ce0b02.title: Rumic Theater
alternateTitles: I grandi capolavori di Rumiko Takahashi Il bouquet rosso
descriptionParagraphs: A sophisticated collection of tales, ranging from the macabre to heartwarming to wacky. The trials and tribulations of daily life.
Volume 1: P no Higeki (released 1994)
1. P no Higeki (The Tragedy of P)
2. Roman no Akindo (The Merchant of Romance)
3. Poi no Ie (The House of Trash)
4. Hachi no Naka (Hidden in the Pottery)
5. Hyakunen no Koi (One Hundred Years of Love)
6. L-size no Shiawase (Extra-Large Sized Happiness)
Volume 2: Senmu no Inu (released 1997)
1. Semmu no Inu (The Director's Dog)
2. Meisou Kazoku Fire (The Astray 'F' Family)
3. Kimi ga Iru dake de (As Long as You Are Here)
4. Chanoma no Love Song (Living Room Love Song)
5. Oyaji Low Teen (Teen Papa)
6. Orei ni Kaete (As Way of Thanks)
Volume 3: Akai Hanataba (released 2005)
1. One Day Dream
2. Graffiti Pop
3. Dutiful Vacation / Giri no Vacance / Holiday-In-Law / A Compulsory Holiday ()
4. Help
5. Red Bouquet
6. Permanent Love
Volume 4: Unmei no Tori (released 2011)
Volume 5: The Witch and the Dinner (released 2019)

5d279916-fef8-446a-b05a-4cd6285eab9a.title: 8 Tales of the ZQN
alternateTitles: Even If I Become a ZQN (Mizusawa Etsuko)
I AM A HERO Koushiki Comic Anthology: 8 Tales of the ZQN
I Am a Hero Untold Creation Story (Yoshimoto Kouji)
I Am Not a Hero (Nogizaka Taro)
She is a Slow Walker (Ito Junji)
The Place Where the Zombies Are (Ishiguro Masakazu)
descriptionParagraphs: An anthology manga containing 8 short stories based around the theme "ZQN" (From "I Am a Hero")

fa525b20-252d-4fa5-9310-5e59b13450e9.title: Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari ~ Girls Side Story
alternateTitles: The Rising of the Shield Hero ~ Girls Side Story
descriptionParagraphs: Raphtalia, a demi-human girl, was living happily with her family and friends. However, she loses her parents to a monster that appeared during a phenomenon called the "Waves of Calamity". Her village that was on the brink of destruction then got plundered by soldiers who came to her village and turned her into a slave. However, her fate made a drastic turn when she meets Naofumi Iwatani, a hero summoned from another world to save this world. The bond between the two gradually deepen as they live together while fighting the monsters from the "Waves of Calamity".
A retelling of the main story in the perspective of Raphtalia

5fd9779c-347a-4f2e-980d-6d903eddc2d4.title: Boku to Emono no Natsuyasumi
alternateTitles: Me and My Prey's Summer Holiday
Summer Vacation for Me and Prey
The Return of the Flower Girl
descriptionParagraphs: 1. Boku to Emono no Natsuyasumi

17 year-old Hatano Mirai's body is extremely weak, so weak that she spent most of her first year of high school in the hospital and had to repeat the year. Unfortunately, due to a cold keeping her in the hospital for a month, she's endanger of repeating again, so she is trying her hardest at her supplementary lessons, when a man literally falls on her hard work?!
2. Boku to Emono wa Haru wo Ou
3. Senaka no Twinkle
4. Sara no Ue no Kanojo
A young girl is sacrificed to appease a hungry and arrogant demon, all for the sake of saving the villagers She was only supposed to fill his empty belly, not worm her way into his heart
5. Kaeribana no Kanojo
Everyday in a park full of cats, a shy boy meets a very special friend
6. Special Edition: Me no Mae ni Hoshi

a75fd897-83bf-4825-a4ea-0632071e000e.title: The Story of a Waitress and Her Customer
descriptionParagraphs: Saki, a college student working at an izakaya, has a crush on Shiraishi, an office worker who is a regular customer. Be brave for your first love today! I gave him a love letter and Shiraishi also has no experience in love?! A heartwarming love comedy

eab47dd9-c5ad-4bf2-b3fe-8952689af299.title: Ojou-sama wa Love Come no Shujinkou ni Naritai!
alternateTitles: A noble girl wants to be a harem protagonist!
Lady Wants to be The Protagonist of a Love Comedy!
descriptionParagraphs: Tsubaki Saionji is a second-year high school girl. Despite her grace and elegance, she hides an embarrassing secret - she absolutely loves mindless ecchi harem love comedies, and always wants to be in the protagonists shoes.
The irony of it all? Without realizing it, she already is a harem protagonist.

39a038c6-9699-44fb-9e8a-5cb12fb4a748.title: Okinawa de Suki ni Natta Ko ga Hougen Sugite Tsura Sugiru
alternateTitles: The Girl I Ended up Falling in Love Within Okinawa Has Too Heavy of a Dialect and Is a Pain to Deal With.
descriptionParagraphs: I, Teruaki Nakamura, transferred to a school Okinawa and developed a crush on a girl named Kiyan-san, but I don't understand her dialect. Higa-san is always helping me by translating the dialect. A slightly different cultural love starts on the southern island.

136a8c13-cf72-427a-8d76-23f1bf070c0e.title: S-Rank Monster no Behemoth Dakedo, Neko to Machigawarete Erufu Musume no Kishi (Pet) Toshite Kurashitemasu
alternateTitles: I Am Behemoth Of The S Rank Monster, But I Am Mistaken As A Cat And I Live As A Pet Of Elf Girl
I'm a Behemoth, an S-Ranked Monster, But Mistaken for a Cat, I Live As an Elf Girl's Pet
Im an S-Rank "Behemoth" Monster, but Im Living as a Knight (Pet) of an Elf Girl
Soy un monstruo de rango S, Behemoth, pero me confundieron con un gato y ahora vivo como el caballero (mascota) de una chica elfa.
descriptionParagraphs: The elven girl Aria is a stunning and swift adventurer. When a small cat-like beast with an adorable face embraces Aria's fruitful chest during a dungeon exploration, she decides to keep it as a pet and names it "Tama". At first sight it's just an average cat, but Aria has yet to notice that Tama is a reincarnated chivalrous former Knight and that its identity is not that of a cat, but of a young monster of the strongest class "Behemoth".

de18ee0b-f9bc-423d-b543-6f6a43024eb6.title: Maou Desu. Onna Yuusha no Hahaoya to Saikon Shita no de, Onna Yuusha ga Giri no Musume ni Narimashita.
alternateTitles: I Am A Demon King. I Got Remarried to A Mother of A Brave Woman, So She Became My Daughter-In-Law.
I, the Demon Lord, got married to the female hero's mother making her my stepdaughter.
descriptionParagraphs: Meet Galtor Luzen, the Demon Lord. Well, the Demon Lord of his own continent, anyway. After his wife passed away, he gradually withdrew from his social life and started to do more of whatever Demon Lords do.
Enter Angelica, the Hero. Heroine. Whatever. Shes a paladin of goodness, who wants nothing more than to defeat the Demon Lord. However, she is no match for him and is utterly defeated.

As Galtor is not a completely evil Demon Lord, he takes Angelica, still unconscious, as well as the other members of her party, back to their families so they can rest their wounds. As he is bringing back Angelica to her home, however, he meets her mother, Reitia - who is the spitting image of his former wife. As he and she bond over tea, Galtors feelings get the better of him, and he proposes to Reitia on the spot. Surprisingly, she accepts.

How will Angelica cope with a literal demon for a stepfather? Can Galtor take care of someone who has taken a blood oath to kill him? Just what are Demon Lords in this world, anyway, for them to nonchalantly treat the battles of good and evil as if they were sports? Read and find out.

16d99766-e3ce-48dd-ae64-f46b482476ab.title: The King of Special Forces With a Negative Emotional Quotient Was Reborn on Campus but Was Unexpectedly Welcomed by Girls?!
alternateTitles: The King of the Special Forces
descriptionParagraphs: When Gu Cheng, the King of the Special Forces, was killed by a mysterious force while avenging his best friend's wife and daughter, he was unexpectedly reborn into someone else's body called Xu Yuan, and even becomes a classmate with his best friend's dead daughter! How will he survive and protect his best friend's wife and daughter this time?

7873dd0e-131f-4f40-8a92-32601713e1da.title: Tenkosaki: The Neat and Pretty Girl at My New School Is a Childhood Friend of Mine Who I Thought Was a Boy
alternateTitles: A Neat and Pretty Girl at the Transfer Destination Was a Childhood Friend Who Used to Think That She Was a Boy and Played With Her.
descriptionParagraphs: I met my childhood friend again, and she had become a beautiful and innocent girl.
"It's been a while, Hayato."
"Haruki, is it?"

In the past, I used to play in the mud with my childhood friend in the countryside, and when I saw him again, there was no trace of the bratty young man I thought he was back then. Only in front of Hayato, she threw away the coat she was wearing and reacted in the same crass way she did back then. The distance between you and me has not changed.

As he cultivated by utilizing the magic that produces from crops to buildings and the knowledge of the previous life , the number of territories increased and became lively.
Moreover, the territory that should have nothing is actually a treasure trove.

Undeterred, he sets his heart on becoming the bottom to his top, always doing his best and looking for opportunities to get closer day after day. Despite turning pale with anger and astonishment at Muratas advances, before long Sunakawa becomes unable to ignore him. descriptionParagraphs: Hime Sakuragaike has secretly been in love with her childhood friend Akira Yonezawa since they were kids, but Hime only recently found out that Akira identifies as female. Although surprised, Hime offers her full support, and this is initially kept secret between them for a few years, but Akira decides to start living as a girl full-time upon starting high school with Hime. However, since Akira garners a certain amount of attention, Hime takes it upon herself to aggressively stick up for Akira whenever necessary. Not wanting Akira to be singled out as an object of ridicule, Hime decides that her only option is to put herself in Akira's shoes.

However, when she gets there she's surrounded by royalty and nobility. Nanari is determined to be the best amongst all the commoners! But the prince who sits beside her is always getting in her way!

After graduating, Nanari successfully became a receptionist at Haare, but each day is far more hectic than what she originally thought would be! On top of all this, that annoying prince who continuously bothered her has found a job and?

descriptionParagraphs: Collection of short stories:
1) Don't Underestimate Me!

Aisaka tends to get in a lot of fights and Takada is the school playboy. On a chance meeting where Aisaka gets beaten to a pulp, Takada offers to carry his bruised body home. There, Takada makes a deal with Aisaka that if he doesn't fight they'll have a sexual relationship.
2) Strange Lover

Masaru and Sugeru are identical twin brothers. Sugeru tends to enjoy using his brothers name to chase skirts and Masaru is the one who always gets the beatings when people come looking for revenge. It's not TOO much of a problem until Masaru meets Masato, a nice guy who really loves Sugeru (who's just using him for money), and it wouldn't be a problem if Masaru wasn't falling for Masato himself.
3) My Heart Really Hurts

Koike, an average student, is best friends with Jinnai, a student who excels. When they get into separate universities Koike still cannot forget what he felt for him, so when Jinnai comes around for a visit Koike jumps on his chance to tell him how he really feels.
4) Isn't Dreaming A Good Thing?

Tomonaga is forced to go to an all boys school when his mother is fed up with his delinquent ways. He expects an torn down rough school, and instead gets a school sparkling with gay pretty boys. Not that he's happy about it. At least his roommate Natsume is normal in a sense.
5) Sorry I'm Such A Pathetic Man

Rather than bumming around all summer his mother orders Yoshimura to get a job. He quickly gets one at a barbecue shop under Sakashita whose grandfather is in the hospital. Yoshimura is surprised by how instantly drawn he is to Sakashita and spends a majority of his time at work trying not to give into his new temptations.
6) I Only Want To Be With You
7) Anyway, Fight Me

With a mere party of five persons, they defeated the Demon Lord regaining the kingdom's peace.

After that journey, Dick Silver, the most balanced between them, racked his brain to not draw public attention. In the end, he decided to become the guild master of a suburban guild as a reward, becoming its twelfth successor. After five years he reached his aim and then became a regular of his own guild's bar. But one day, as he was drinking at the bar as always, the daughter of a certain aristocrat came to pay him a visit.

In a twist of fate, she reincarnated as a pampered daughter of a rich family. Just when she thought that she would finally be able to a simple and carefree life, she suddenly realizes that the adored talented young miss of the capital city was actually not loved by either of her parents? Ye Jinsu said to herself, "...at least there're still some perks. At least I'm rich and I can have any man I want, heck there's even this one man that won't stop pestering me all the time." That same man who pestered her would go on to ask her, "Young Miss, I will trade a thousand taels of gold for your hand in marriage." "No deal." "How about my empire in exchange for your heart?"

Trying to avoid betraying his girlfriend's trust in him, Naoya thinks up a "solution" to make both girls happytwo-timing. Naturally, Saki rebuffs this idea, but through Naoya's and Nagisa's persistence, she reluctantly submits.
With this, a three-way affair begins between Naoya, his girlfriend, and his "other" girlfriend, as they develop a relationship that deviates from the social norm.

"Please, use me."

Lizette, a count's daughter, is a "Recaller", or a holder of previous lives' memories, and she is on her fourth life.  In her past lives, always on her 20th birthday, she would be killed and eaten by a demon. So to live a long life in this one, Lizette retreated to a remote countryside sanctuary, where monsters don't appear, living quietly and peacefully.
However, one day, she, once again, met a noble boy whom she saved in her childhood, Ralph. Somehow, he had become the country's hero, who toppled a demonic king.
If it may be possible to avoid death by Ralph's side... With this in mind, Lizette accepted his proposal.
"Even if your life is switched, I will always protect you, Miss Lizette."
While bewildered by Ralph's exceedingly heavy affection, Lizette approaches the truth of her repeating deaths. Will Lizette be able to live pass her 20th birthday unharmed this time?!
From now, the serious romantic comedy between the heroine who doesn't want to die and the intensely loving yandere hero begins!

descriptionParagraphs: Sano, a pure high school boy, is a virgin who wants to be popular among the ladies. In an unexpected turn of events, he meets the handsome and trendy Fujita, a university student who he respects as his master. When they happen to meet again in town, Fujitas eyes were swollen with tears from a fresh break-up. While hearing Fujita out, Sano learns that hes gay, and whats more, Fujita makes a strong suggestion for Sano to lose his virginity to him!

2d5e6c12-e494-4389-ac8b-947b7e7f8f61.title: It called an Element!
descriptionParagraphs: The girl named Luna is here!
The girl with ne name Luna is a demon who want to take revenge of the city Haeveros because they optained her diamons called Crystal which are protecting the city from demon beeing.
Luna destroyed these Crystals als is now taking over the city.
But theres a small flame even in the darkest place.
Her name is Christine Chebkey!
If you like to translate it you can translate it from German to English if you like to support the Artist.
Note: The Artist said she was going to take a Little break.
Im sorry About it!

d865893e-424d-406e-8945-3618087bb7b8.title: Uragiri wa Boku no Namae o Shitteiru
alternateTitles: Uragiri wa Boku no Namae o Shitteiru
Uragiri wa Boku no Namae wo Shitte Iru
Uragiri wa Boku no Namae wo Shitteiru
descriptionParagraphs: From Yen Press:

Abandoned as a baby and raised in an orphanage, the kind-hearted high-schooler Sakuragi Yuuki is driven by a need to find the reason for his existence. Plagued by mysterious dreams, Yuuki also possesses the strange ability to read the deepest, darkest thoughts of anyone he touches.

As both the dreams and his powers intensify, there appears before him a beautiful young man named Zess, whose face tugs on Yuuki's memory. He warns Yuuki not to venture outside on Walpurgis Night, the eve of the blood-red moon, which invites death.
But when Yuuki's compassion leads him to disobey Zess's order, has he carelessly thrown his life away before he's even given himself the chance to find out the very reason for it?

9ce44d6c-034c-4daf-abe6-ecf952230557.title: Namaiki na Ryouken no Shitsukekata
alternateTitles: The Training Of The Impudent Dog
descriptionParagraphs: The Shinjuku police station's detective Ao, who had been tracking a drug dealer for half a year, was caught by a man that appeared suddenly. The problem is that Ao inhaled some of the evidence by accident. A young man by the name of Noe helps Ao, who has lost consciousness after the fact. Ao is reprimanded by his boss and receives sarcastic remarks from his co-workers. At that time, Ao receives a photograph. That photograph shows a dead Naji, who was Ao's S. It's hunt or be hunted; eat or be eaten The heated race of the yakuza men.

9427736c-1859-4a71-801b-e6717049b903.title: Azur Lane - Kimi no Namae wo Torimodose (Doujinshi)
descriptionParagraphs: **Please support the author/artist patreon:**

574528a4-f215-4766-8051-507be352ccda.title: Na*Na*Ki!!
descriptionParagraphs: The youngest of seven sisters, Nanaki's goal is to "grow another 20cm and become an adult." Now she's a senior in high school and still baffles her friends with her childish ways. But simple sincerity is Nanaki's greatest power, and friendship is the most important thing in the world to her. Problems like volunteering to be class president won't stand in her way

c733b54b-91c0-4be4-ac91-270943e85929.title: Natsumeki!!
descriptionParagraphs: "I wanted to create a summery, sparkling youth." - And so the theme is "yosakoi*"!!

For the sake of her younger sister's medical treatment, Natsume moves from her home in Tokyo to Shikoku. In a place where no one knows her, she decides to make her high school debut as a "cool beauty"! This determined Natsume is approached by the wild child-like Yudai saying, "Join my team"??
Eeh!!? What do you mean by team!!?

83dec322-3f40-4ccf-97a7-a9de8230a477.title: Sakura Namiki
descriptionParagraphs: From MU:
This manga is quite oldit's from 1957. It centers around three members of the table tennis club at an all-girl school. Though it may not quite be yuri, it's a precursor to current yuri manga.

175ae5cf-fa0b-4bd5-b927-d22f6888b10a.title: Namikibashi Doori - Aoba Jitenshaten
alternateTitles: Aoba Bicycle Shop on Namikibashi Street
descriptionParagraphs: A simple slice-of-life manga about a young girl and her father who runs a small bicycle shop.

a9d97564-8661-483e-a869-dc70ee1cc966.title: Choushinri Genshou Nouryokusha Nanaki
descriptionParagraphs: Nanaki survives a car accident to discover he is psychic. Recruited into an organization that solves cases with psychic powers, Nanaki's average life quickly turns into one of adventure and intrigue.

153f42f0-9a60-4bb4-9a54-78713e1cfea8.title: Ojou to Nanahiki no Inu
alternateTitles: Young Miss and the Seven Dogs
descriptionParagraphs: This story takes place in a world where humans and beastmen coexist. Our protagonist, a Dog beastman, was a former gangster who's fallen on hard times, living on the streets and scraping by on what he can get.

On one particular rainy day, he tries to fall asleep in an alley before being found by an eccentric 'Yamato Nadeshiko' type of girl. She offers him a home to sleep in, in exchange for him becoming her bodyguard. He doesn't think much of it until he sees her home and it's explained to him by the servants in it that she's the daughter of a Yakuza boss and has a sadistic personality. On top of all that, almost all her servants are beastmen as well!

7e40baa9-bceb-437a-a026-db9b49bb527a.title: Joushi no Kuse ni Namaiki da

10dacde6-aa94-41af-83ab-3a57fcd5e4eb.title: Mahoko no Kuse ni Namaiki da!
alternateTitles: Mahoko no Kuse ni Namaiki Da
descriptionParagraphs: Mahoko's been with her buddy, Chise, since the day that she was born. He's cool, good-looking, and a hit with the girls. But, Chise has a secret that only Mahoko knows ? he likes boys. He was always leading her around by the nose until one day, he grabs her and kisses her!!

ca3cfc7e-3da7-41b0-bffb-b2a84d03cec3.title: My Own Contract Angel
descriptionParagraphs: After being traumatised from getting forcefully outed, Yeonho, a closeted gay, is a "single-for-life" who has never dated anyone. One day, Yeonho gets hit by a shooting star, and he woke up to see someone, who calls himself "Cupid", sharing his bed! The strange man promised to end Yeonho's one-sided crushes, but will he really?

3365dc3d-5afa-405f-af1b-df14c29b00e6.title: Miiko Desu!
descriptionParagraphs: Miiko brings us to see how things are from the eyes of a 4th grade child. This one will be fun to read, not only for kids, but also for adults who want to remember how everything was from the child's perspective.

c0d0c058-a72d-4194-8f0c-48c40f959131.title: Namaiki Hierarchy
descriptionParagraphs: From middle school, high school to university, Yui's kouhai, Mikki, has always been chasing after him. Even though Mikki nags him all the time, he seems fond of Yui Unconsciously, Yui started feeling a sense of superiority over Mikki and he ends up getting ahead of himself, hence provoking Mikki?!

9a6410f9-37b6-418d-937d-9b1705bd18b7.title: Kantai Collection -KanColle- Kuchikukan no kuseni namaiki da!! (Doujinshi)
alternateTitles: Kantai Collection -KanColle- dj - Kuchikukan no kuse ni Namaiki da!!
Kantai Collection -KanColle- dj Kuchikukan no kuseni namaiki da!!

7ce22c9e-5939-435e-b067-64ce659bb3b3.title: Hazure Skill Gacha de Tsuihou Sareta Ore wa, Wagamama Osananajimi wo Zetsuen Shi Kakusei Suru
alternateTitles: After Being Banished For Having The Trash Skill "Gacha", I Came To My Senses And Broke Off Relations With My Selfish Childhood Friend
descriptionParagraphs: Crest was born as the fifth son of a duke. However, as the fifth son, he was in no position to talk. His childhood friend and also his fiance, Ellis, treated him just like a slave. And on Crest's coming-of-age ceremony, he received a skill called "Gacha." Yet, he wasn't able to learn how to use it and was banished away from his home. Banished into the forest full of monsters, Crest began to understand the power "Gacha." And then, Crest made up his mind. He will definitely survive and get back on his feet.

756ce634-7895-4068-a9a7-0733c9ecb088.title: Bitchy Mean Girls
descriptionParagraphs: The sweet and bitchy daily lives of rich girls and their best friends.
**NOTICE : THIS MANHUA DOSENT HAVE A FIX UPDATING SCHEDULE. IT UPDATES ONCE PER 1 OR 2 MONTHS. SO TO SAY, IT DEPENDS ON THE ARTIST, IF THEY FEEL LIKE UPDATING OR NOT**

d1a950db-4296-4deb-a295-8e20c1b8b65f.title: Persona 3
descriptionParagraphs: A teenager who was orphaned as a young boy returns to the city of his childhood. Shortly after transferring to Gekkoukan High School, he is attacked by Shadows  creatures that feed on the minds of their victims. He soon discovers that he shares a special ability with other students at his new school. From them, he learns of the "Dark Hour," a hidden time that exists between one day and the next, swarming with Shadows. He joins the Specialized Extracurricular Execution Squad (SEES), and with his new friends, confronts the threat of the Shadows.
Based on the PlayStation 2 game of the same name.

d8696cf4-0de0-40b6-90ac-2030bbc2d37a.title: Yoshinatsu
descriptionParagraphs: Yoshinatsu is a one-shot about a friend that will not be forgotten.

2163c710-d78f-49ea-a1cf-79a03ac6a8a3.title: Persona - Tsumi to Batsu
alternateTitles: Shin Megami Tensei: Persona - Tsumi to B
descriptionParagraphs: This story is a spin-off to the Persona 2 duology of games by Atlus starring a young man named Kazumi Kiba. Kazumi thought he was good friends with a boy he had known for ten years, Rihito. One day, while they were out in town together looking for a shop selling masks for their school's masquerade ball, Rihito suddenly disappears. Kazumi drops out of school and starts looking for him, and will soon set foot in a totally new world.

99b8eaeb-9041-4bfd-8eb7-d72addc88eb7.title: Megami no Kafeterasu
alternateTitles: The Cafe Terrace of the Goddesses
descriptionParagraphs: Kasukabe Hayato has been accepted to Tokyo U on his first try. Receiving news of his grandmother's death, he returns to his childhood home, Cafe Terrace Familia, for the first time in three years to find five strange girls there who claim to be "Grandma's Family"! Hayato's unexpected life in a seaside town with these five girls of fate begins here!
In this handsome harem under one roof by Koji Seo of *Suzuka*, *Kimi no Iru Machi*, and *Fuuka*, which girl will you fall in love with? A seaside love comedy with too many heroines!

e17122ae-681c-4f99-a945-f37a11165811.title: Megami no Sprinter
descriptionParagraphs: Takase is the opposite of his brother. He's weaker and struggles in school. He recently moved into his married brother's house in order to receive coaching to improve his physical health. The coach, also known as the "Venus of Track," is none other than his sister-in-law. The Venus of Track is researching and developing a new technique to improve male performance by testosterone management. In other words, manipulation of sexual desire. She has dubbed it "Absolute Obedience" and Takase must undergo it to improve himself. Takase's life is in for a dramatic change

a3cf1860-52ed-40ad-adf8-bb9fbbe5f654.title: Mega Maiden
alternateTitles: Mega Maiden & The Chop Chop Princess
descriptionParagraphs: As Mega Maiden, Isis Cook is empowered with a superhuman rack and superhuman strength. Along with her BFF Delaney Bell A.K.A The Chop Chop Princess, he gets a crash course in superheroing. unfortunately for her, every big-name superhero is a complete and utter douche bags.

50a8407c-7aaa-402b-8fd8-bb6e647911a5.title: Megami no Libra
descriptionParagraphs: Tsumire Yuuki, a high school student suddenly lost her mother. The person appearing before her at this time is the lawyer Koudai Hino, telling her that she's actually the granddaughter of a wealthy estate owner. After being taken in by her grandfather, and living a life of luxury, Tsumire's heart starts to waver towards Koudai that's always by her side.
Pt-Br:

Yuuki Tsumire foi criada por sua me solteira, que sempre ensinou a ela para sempre continuar sorrindo, no importasse o quanto fosse difcil. As duas eram uma famlia, at a me da Tsumire morrer por causa de uma doena. Logo aps isso ela descobre que tem uma famlia que ela nem conhecia, uma famlia fria e rica. Tsumire agora precisa viver com essa famlia, mesmo que parea que nenhum deles deseja que ela viva l. Ela no precisa trocar de escola, por isso ainda tem os seus amigos, mas ela no quer causar mais problemas para eles, por isso sempre guarda os seus problemas para s mesma. Mas para a surpresa dela, um advogado da famlia chamado Hino, se torna o seu "apoio sentimental", mas as aes da Tsumire fazem parecer que ela queria que ele fosse algo a mais

b4d803e5-d825-456e-bb0e-77f05ffc1e63.title: Shin Megami Tensei - Kahn
descriptionParagraphs: Six months ago, Karukozaka High School was sucked into the demon world, and in the ensuing chaos, only two survivors emerged: Nobu, who defeated the Demon Lord that took over the school, and Yumi, who possesses latent demon powers of her own.

Although they're both trying to put the incident behind them, the gateway to the Underworld remains open, and soon Nobu finds himself battling demons right on the streets of Tokyo. The reason for this infestation is simple: a secret organization is trying to establish a Demon Kingdom on Earth by summoning demons through the gateway.

Nobu and Yumi are the only people to have been to the Underworld and survived, so they may have the power to stop the infestation but before that can even happen, they'll have to find each other first.

b1f57b6d-1709-4dfb-8a5d-c7658eba1051.title: Ah! My Job-Hunting Goddess
descriptionParagraphs: In the wake of the recent recession, Keiichi's motorcycle shop has been experiencing financial difficulties. Belldandy enlists the help of her sisters and begins job-hunting to support him! Will she be able to find work? Only the gods can tell!

4aecf422-7afe-405f-b2d4-e5b80a1872ac.title: Megane, Tokidoki, Yankee-kun
descriptionParagraphs: After being in a middle school full of Yankees and being humiliated by them all the time, Momose decides to change her appearance when entering high school; however, her clumsiness keeps getting the best of her, so she struggles to fit in. All she wants is to get away from the bad guys and it seems like she finally found a club to belong to, but the only other member of this club is not quite what he seems

830b4cdd-df77-4a48-975a-aa2bc0684738.title: Striving for the Luxury Liner
descriptionParagraphs: After falling into the ocean, Wataru Toyoumi, finds himself reincarnated in another world! Armed with a skill to allow him to summon boats, he plans to get rich and live a happy life aboard his very own luxury liner.

6d6d9fda-5cd3-40ac-948b-776b1a1a0eb1.title: Suki na Ko ga Megane wo Wasureta
alternateTitles: The Girl I Like Forgot Her Glasses
descriptionParagraphs: Komura is a middle school boy who is head-over-heels in love with his next-seat neighbor Mie, a girl with terrible eyesight who just can't get used to carrying her glasses, often leaving them at home, or accidentally breaking them. He opts to help her as much as he possibly can, and through those efforts, she begins getting acquainted with his kindness. Will she reciprocate?
**Links:**

88f98f21-bae9-4057-8a35-e0a7d427f1b8.title: Megami-ryou no Ryoubo-kun
descriptionParagraphs: Nagumi Koushi is a 12-year-old boy who was abandoned by his broke father after their house caught on fire, leaving him to roam the streets penniless. Then one day, a girl named Minerva who finds him lying on the sidewalk takes him to a womens college dormitory, one known for housing troublesome residents, and asks him to be their "Dormitory Mother." Surrounded by older women, forced to deal with their idiosyncrasies, Koushi starts his new (somewhat ecchi) life!

a3ab9f36-ac31-4f79-b2a5-7a304d0af9ce.title: Being With You Means the World to Me
alternateTitles: My World is Complete Because of You
descriptionParagraphs: The journey of a very sweet, fluffy and warm couple! The author, Da Ning, recorded 10 years of her relationship with her lover, Lin Zhi Min. The two love birds fell in love at first sight in the university's garden. Time and distance tested their relationship but they used their love to overcome these challenges and build their own world. "No matter how big the world is, the sight that suits me the most, is you."

7dc3f66f-4d6e-4030-bd6c-6a4d699a7f06.title: Bijin Onna Joushi Takizawa-san
descriptionParagraphs: Kouta Takeda is a young office worker, who at the entry level at XOX Corporation is put under the direct supervision of Kyouko Takizawa, a stunning and voluptuous woman with a fearsome reputation at the company as an inflexible and cruel boss, but Takeda has the privilege of finding out that Takizawa is no iron lady, and that she's no stranger to kindness where it's dispensed.

9937f7da-7913-49cb-a354-2e4ecd9cbd52.title: Shinja Zero no Megami-sama to Hajimeru Isekai Kouryaku
alternateTitles: Clearing an Isekai with the Zero-Believers Goddess
The Weakest Mage among the Classmates
descriptionParagraphs: After his class gets buried alive on their way back from a school trip, 18 year old Makoto Takatsuki and class get transported to another world. Unlike the rest of his classmates who gained powerful abilities, Makoto barely gains any power. "This other world is unbalanced!". With the threat of a great Demon Lord rising again and a goddess with zero followers, can Makoto make his way through this new world and clear the isekai!?

0f932cd1-7984-40c9-875c-46f3f5eee3f5.title: Will The Undine Fall In Love Again Today?
alternateTitles: La diosa del agua Undine hoy tambin enamorar?
Akankah Sang Dewi Air (Undine) Jatuh Cinta Lagi Hari Ini?
Mizu Megami (Undine) wa Kyou mo Koi wo Suru ka?
Undine wa kyou mo koi wo suru ka?
descriptionParagraphs: The kingdom of Rahasa is a desert city that is experiencing a drought spanning generations. The last rain was an eternity ago and the sky is clear of clouds. The only salvation of Rahasa's residents is Aquarea, a girl with the ability to create water. But as her powers begin to weaken, what can her friend Asha do?

5a3c3942-497e-4030-81a2-60bb1fb751cb.title: Hayasegawa-kun to Megami na Onee-san
descriptionParagraphs: A beautiful older lady regularly visits the coffee-shop where high school student Hayasegawa-kun works. He doesn't know her name, her job, or where she lives, but she is nevertheless his "ideal woman".
**Links:**

bfd76e18-140e-4a54-979f-e88ea0b3d3c0.title: The Knight Commander Wants to Monopolize the Former Glasses Girl
descriptionParagraphs: I was caught up in a trip to another world and was treated as a nuisance, but the person who helped me was the commander of the Second Knights, Leon, who was super strong and handsome! He was blunt but kind and always took care of me. But why does he get so nervous when I take off my glasses?
Melissa's popular high-tension love fantasy is finally available in comic form!
Underneath the thick-rimmed glasses is a beautiful girl! The misfortune girl is loved with all her might by the knight commander who is full of possessiveness!

8a7992ca-634f-4625-ad41-8d2e75003f5b.title: Dad Is a Hero, Mom Is a Spirit, I'm a Reincarnator.
alternateTitles: My Father is a Hero, my Mother is a Spirit and the Daughter (Me) is a Reincarnator.
descriptionParagraphs: Well, I was reincarnated! And my father is a former hero? And my mother is a queen of the spirits!? With my knowledge of my past life and my powers in this world I'll protect my family's happiness!

3013e1e9-6e0f-4166-8113-6abdac466070.title: Watashi no Okaa-sama wa Tsuihou sareta Moto Akuyaku Reijou Deshita
alternateTitles: My Mother Was a Prosecuted Ex-Villainess
My Mother Was a Prosecuted Ex-villainess - The Ascendance of an Ugly Four-eyed Commoner
descriptionParagraphs: "Your identity must never be revealed. Your eyes and your hair would inconvenience both your mother and the people of the kingdom"

The mother of Ashley, who is a fifteen-year-old girl, was called a villainess, got prosecuted, and then kidnapped. As result, she has conceived a child, Ashley, who was later told that she shared the same eye and hair color as the man who had kidnapped her mother. She wears glasses and an Alice band that use the power of magic to make her look disagreeable in others' eyes, and thus gets called an "ugly four-eyes." Unable to make any friends, Ashley used to lead an academy life of loneliness and solitude
However, after her encounter with a mysterious creature, the crown prince grows interested in her?

878634d2-ea39-4001-a4bf-31458020d16a.title: Akuyaku Reijou Level 99
alternateTitles: Villainess Level 99 ~I May Be the Hidden Boss but I'm Not the Demon Lord~
descriptionParagraphs: I reincarnated as the "Villainess Eumiella" from an RPG Otome game. In the main story, Eumiella is merely a side character, but after the ending, she re-enters the story as the Hidden Boss, a character boasting high stats on par with the heroes! Lighting a fire in my gamer's soul, and taking advantage of being left on my own in my parent's territory, I trained, trained, and trained! As a result of my training by the time I enrolled in the academy, I managed to reach level 99. Though I had planned to live out my days as inconspicuously and peacefully as possible, soon after entering the school, I'm suspected by the Heroine and Love Interests of being the "Demon Lord"?
Based on a popular web novel of seeking a peaceful life, a fantasy story of the strongest villainess!

72dbebb1-bf6b-4f86-be38-88024c220aa1.title: Shitsuji ga Megane wo Hazusuyoru
alternateTitles: The Night the Butler Takes Off his Glasses
descriptionParagraphs: From Good Girls Scan BL:

Kounosuke is the son of the Sumeragi industrial group and is a playboy. Hitsuji, the head butler, always chastises him for his bad attitude. Wanting to exact revenge on his strict and handsome butler, Kounosuke slips aphrodisiac into his black tea. Even after watching him for a while, there was no change, and so to test the drug's effectiveness, Kounosuke drank it himself. As he does, the medicine takes effect immediately and causes him to become sexually excited...?!
In addition, the compilation of ""Honey Love Butler"", the romance between a young and extremely popular violinist nobleman with a servant, both with different social statuses.

ac4deac1-93fa-4d29-81b9-6fa5cacfc07d.title: Fate/Grand Order - Megami-sama to Tea Time (Doujinshi)
alternateTitles: Fate/Grand Order dj - Megami-sama to Tea Time

53823ad0-e3a9-42d1-aab0-e1b6840b7fa3.title: Ore no Megane wa Tabun Sekai Seifuku Dekiru to Omou.
alternateTitles: My Glasses Will Be Able to Conquer the Whole World, I Suppose.
descriptionParagraphs: Eil is an apprentice hunter from the village Albat who hates being the target of attention. Upon becoming 15, at the Ceremony of Determination that he needs to go through to be acknowledged as an adult, he is determined to possess the "Talent for Glasses."
For glasses? What does that even mean?
But gradually, Eil discovers the countless possibilities hidden within his glasses, one at a time.
"I think these glasses might actually enable me to conquer the whole world. Not that I'm going to do it, though."
Thus begins the bizarre glasses life of Eil, the young glasses man.

9bf8c6ee-b735-4e3f-966e-6a31bc03aa24.title: Goddess Creation System
descriptionParagraphs: Otaku Xiaxi committed suicide because a guy in a game exposed her true identity. However, she didn't die and instead time-traveled to a world with countless handsome men. Prepare to see how an otaku transforms into a beautiful goddess!
PTBR:

Pela personalidade e aparncia simples, o namorado da Xiaxi terminou com ela. Por ter sido introvertida, Xiaxi entra para o mundo dos jogos online, onde ela  conhecida como uma Deusa. Um dia ela encontra o namorado online dela, que fica to chocado pela aparncia real dela que expe o rosto real da Deusa nos fruns, onde o bullying comea a ser muito para ela e Xiaxi comete suicdio. Mas ela no morre e acaba indo parar em um mundo cheio de homens lindos. Preparem-se para ver como uma Otaku se transforma em uma linda Deusa.

138bec6a-f95b-48b9-8c55-fe5a254ac819.title: What It Means to be You
descriptionParagraphs: In exchange for clearing off the royal familys huge debt, Princess Violet was sent to marry Winter, the dukes illegitimate son.
Ive never seen such a wonderful man before in my life. Although Violet fell in love with her husband at first sight, their arranged marriage was destined to fail from the beginning.
If it were easy, I wouldnt have come here. Just this once together
Do you realize how much money has been moved while youve stood here, wasting my time?
Three years later, Violet wasnt sure such a busy man would even bother to attend her funeral. When she decided to end it all
Whats going on Violet blankly stared at herself in the bedrooms full-body mirror. The person staring back at her was her husband, Winter Blooming. Why did they switch bodies?
I guess Ive really gone crazy now.

ecb774d8-d124-404f-9c2c-263e08761b1f.title: Mousou Megane - Digital Colored Comics
descriptionParagraphs: Imagine what you could do if you had glasses that could see through the clothes of that cute classmate youve had a crush on. Or that young teacher that you daydreamed about the entire time during class. Maybe your long time female friend that you never had the courage to ask out. If you could see their beautiful body without them having a clue, what would you do? This is every guys fantasy played out.

0296dc0b-7635-4154-927a-33c2244c4503.title: Yahari Ore no Seishun Love Come wa Machigatteiru.: Monologue
alternateTitles: My Youth Romantic Comedy Is Wrong As I Expected. - Monologue
descriptionParagraphs: Hikigaya Hachiman, a boy with a distorted personality, is brought to the "Service Club", led by a beautiful and harsh girl named Yukinoshita Yukino, by his academic advisor. Hilarity ensues as the isolated boy, through his many mistakes, begins to reshape himself and those around him.

79afd0e8-d0c2-4d3b-a913-520b26ee6e81.title: Haishinchuu Megami Channel! E, Kore Baimei desu no!?
descriptionParagraphs: Elf reverse isekai'd herself into Japan because she's horny. Tsundere goddess comes along to fix things, but a popular chuunibyou youtuber, a succubus, a psychic and a dragon also get added to the mix. How will Akahito, a bottom of the barrel youtuber, and the useless goddess fare?

dfa4aed9-37d6-4530-b479-62d8998640ba.title: Megane to Koi to Aoi Tori
descriptionParagraphs: Kei, who loves to read shoujo manga and romance novels, is a high school student yearning for love. However, he understands that his unpopularity doesn't make him fated for love. If he were just as handsome as his childhood friend, Kiyoshi, love would probably come easily Thinking of this, Kei gets envious of Kiyoshi.

ca29b611-0f7b-4450-95c9-1659f0f6f5a0.title: Kare ga Megane wo Hazusutoki
alternateTitles: Kare ga Megane o Hazusu Toki
Kare ga Megane wo Hazusu Toki
When He Takes Off His Glasses (ASOU Mitsuaki)
descriptionParagraphs: "Could I take the place of my brother?" When Tomoe's best friend, Ichita develops an interest in the new transfer student, it affects Tomoe. Not knowing the reason for this, a corner of his heart slows. In the wake of all that, he becomes close with Ichita's younger brother, Kenji. The two of them meet, but one day, on top of pointing out Tomoe's feelings for Ichita, Kenji also confesses his own feelings. It's a story full of waves and waves of emotions and angst youth.

4) By Akiduki Wataru

1f041189-ff20-4aed-9ef5-38e1ed8202e1.title: Noraneko to Yubikiri
alternateTitles: Pinky Swear with a Stray Cat
descriptionParagraphs: Ayato is a part time worker who lives alone, struggling to survive. One day, his mother suddenly appears only to leave his young sister under his care. Ayato then goes to City Hall to ask for help, as he wants to leave his sister in a nursery school while he works. At that place, the one who had to help Ayato was Haruna, a serious and hard-working employee, but instead of listening to him and without knowing about Ayato's circumstances, began to preach saying "Even stray cats are more responsible with their children than you are." Ayato snapped saying "What do you know about me?"

A hard working employee and a hard worker who is underemployed, gradually heal each other's past wounds and become fascinated with each other. What kind of promise will these two people make when they have experienced hard times in the past? Can they trust in each other?

37e8bcef-918f-4220-ac81-53f3a5919304.title: Noraneko to Ookami
descriptionParagraphs: Mishina Tamaki is an orphan girl who left her village to study in the city. On a hot afternoon, while she was looking for a place to stay, she fainted. Upon waking up, she realized she was picked up by a playful rock musician. The story of their cohabitation that could (probably) turn into love, starts!

d9139a5c-5fd1-418d-8ad4-a602a0b053b5.title: Noraneko to Hidamari
alternateTitles: Stray Cat and the Sunny Spot
descriptionParagraphs: Touko is a shy girl who loves animals, but because of her gloomy appearance, they always run away. One day, has a casual encounter with Akito, a boy who has always watched her from far and who  will help her get closer to them?

ff4c281f-cadb-4684-bd56-77313bca3e02.title: Touhou - Tokaiha Neko to Noraneko no Hanashi. (Doujinshi)
alternateTitles: Touhou dj - A Story About a City Cat and a Stray Cat
Touhou dj - Tokaiha Neko to Noraneko no Hanashi.
Touhou Project dj - A Story About a City Cat and a Stray Cat

9e0c53c7-16bd-4f98-affe-de4408c4338e.title: Hikaeme ni Itte mo, Kore wa Ai
alternateTitles: To Say The Least, This is Love
descriptionParagraphs: One day, a serious student named Risa, saves a wounded delinquent on her way home from cram school. Now, that delinquent Zen is following her around!! What will she do?

aadfb8fb-7474-4d04-ad68-42b854f5b001.title: Jigoku Kozou
descriptionParagraphs: A mysterious old woman appears before doctor Rasetsu Emma, who has recently lost his son in an accident. She says she can bring Daio back to life. After agreeing to this sinister proposal, Daio returns to his father, but to Rasetsu's horror, he is half decomposed and inhuman. To make him human again, he needs fresh human organs. Rasetsu does everything he can to reincarnate his son, but Daio just turns into a different kind of monster. No one can stop him as he continues to feed his hunger, claiming victim after victim.

73be335c-bcdf-4668-b757-3730010932e2.title: Jigoku Mushi o Kuu! Oninbo
alternateTitles: Oninbo and the Bugs from Hell
descriptionParagraphs: That?s because his favorite snacks are grotesque Bugs from Hell. These creatures live in the hearts of people, where they grow fat and hideous until they are ready to devour the very souls that nourish them. Oninbo can smell a bug a mile away, and will risk anything to get his hands on a ripe, juicy specimen. But he?s not the only one with a bug appetite. Mamushinbo, his demon rival, is also after the Bugs from Hell.
The Hino Horror series:
Hino Horror Volume 1: The Red Snake ( Akai Hebi)
Hino Horror Volume 2: The Bug Boy ( Dokumushi Kozou)

Hino Horror Volume 13: Zipangu Night
Hino Horror Volume 14: Skin and Bone

b252e636-0143-42d7-903c-de0c9772d5fb.title: Itsudemo Jitaku Ni Kaerareru Ore Wa, Isekai De Gyoushounin O Hajimemashita
alternateTitles: I Can Always Go Home, so I Started as a Peddler in Another World
descriptionParagraphs: "Won't I be able to get filthy rich if I use this skill?"

Continually exploited at work, Amata Shirou quits his job and moves to his grandma's house. When he finds out that it's connected to another world, he comes up with a plan to set up a business selling Japanese goods.
The story of a man getting rich using his skill that converts the currency of the other world to Japanese yen and so forth.

b461d615-1bed-4dea-b1fb-99d862c98ea6.title: Daddy at Work and at Home
alternateTitles: Papa With a Gap Between Work and Home
descriptionParagraphs: At work he's smooth and cool, but at home he's a total softie?!
A collection of short stories about a doting father and his precious family!
Author:

d4a49028-1aa5-4422-ad5d-729b20d0dc4f.title: Jigoku Kurayami Hana mo Naki
descriptionParagraphs: A young man who can see peoples sins in the form of youkai gets employed at a sort of odds-and-ends agency run by supernatural beings.

b6116025-1a94-4f32-9c9b-aa341f3950f0.title: Hagure Idol Jigokuhen
alternateTitles: Booty Royale: Never Go Down Without A Fight!
descriptionParagraphs: This is the story of Misora Haebaru, an 18-year-old karate expert from Okinawa who went to Tokyo to enter the entertainment industry in hopes of supporting her family. She gets tricked into being a gravure idol who wears lewd clothing and is forced eventually to enter the AV world, but she won't go down without a fight!

a3b6acf5-9815-4f83-b79a-e5f21e22a1a5.title: Kuro Elf ni Kawareta Ore no Dungeon Seikatsu: Sanshoku Furo to Jigoku-tsuki
descriptionParagraphs: One day, a "calamity" comes and destroys the city, killing both the protagonist Kruz and his sister Arti. However, Before Kruz dies, he sees a dark elf girl named Enju whom he had met before. The girl says. What do you want, to end your life silently like this.... or to become a shinigami who kills "calamities" ?

96f69304-ab9a-43ce-83cc-8fe90958c5b3.title: Hana ni Arashi
descriptionParagraphs: Even though her body has an unusual ability, Kunimi Riko is still (trying to be) a normal high school girl. One day, a guy suddenly comes to see her. Hes Tachibana Ran, the heir of the world-leading super-millionaire Tachibana family! A high tension romance between Ran, who suddenly proposed, and Riko, who turned him down.
Extra:
- Jigoku Kokyuu no Hitsuyou (Vol.1)

Kiyoharu was trying to nap when a girl kissed him because she thought he was dead. He later learns that Touko, the girl, is always kissing someone in response to not being able to breathe and feeling suffocated.
- Fureru Ondo (Vol.2)

Kashuu hates being touched because of his past experiences. He will only let Sayuri-sensei, the biology teacher, treat his wounds. To him, Sayuri-sensei's touch is precise and practical without bring up bad memories

a4b39b6e-a448-4644-a540-64ceff1d8305.title: Jibaku Shounen Hanako-kun
descriptionParagraphs: "Hanako-san, Hanako-san are you there?"

At Kamome Academy, rumors abound about the school's Seven Mysteries, one of which is Hanako-san. Said to occupy the third stall of the third floor girls' bathroom in the old school building, Hanako-san grants any wish when summoned. Nene Yashiro, an occult-loving high school girl who dreams of romance, ventures into this haunted bathroom but the Hanako-san she meets there is nothing like she imagined! Kamome Academy's Hanako-san is a boy!
**Note:** Volume 0 includes the original pilot version of Jibaku Shounen Hanako-kun and the debut oneshot of Aida Iro - Dear My Living Dead.

cb77e4a6-3921-43b9-9d64-7d78cd3205ce.title: Jigokuraku
descriptionParagraphs: Gabimaru the Empty, a former ninja assassin known feared as a heartless husk of a man, spends his days on death row wondering when an executioner skilled enough to so much as harm him will arrive, as he thinks nothing of seeing an end to his meaningless existence Or so he thought. Then the lady executioner, Asaemon the Beheader, rekindles his hope with an astounding proposition. If he ever wishes to see his beloved wife again, he is, under the auspices of the shogunate, to embark on a perilous voyage to the mysterious mystic island said to house the elixir of immortality. Should he be the one among many rival death-row fiends and scoundrels to find the elixir, he'll earn a full exoneration, and, more importantly, a chance at an ordinary married life with the light of his lifethe woman who made the world seem not so ugly. What awaits them is a journey like no other!

c5cfd48a-c00a-4948-945f-177645e09d57.title: Jigoku e Michizure
descriptionParagraphs: 1-3) Travelling Companion to Hell
A fledgling magician attempts to summon a demonic familiar. What he gets is a sultry, slutty, poncy imp.
4) Love and Hypnotism
Two guys and some hypnosis.
5) My Alice
A man attempts to artificially creates a human to his ideals, but it does not go as he envisioned
6) Love From the Bath House
A receptionist at a bath house has a crush on a certain customer, who's been visiting a lot lately
7) I Was Made For
A boy and his brother have a complicated relationship. (incest)
8) Equinoctial Week's Lover
A young man's first kiss with his boyfriend is awkwardly interrupted by a phone call, telling him his boyfriend has passed away. (supernatural)
9) To The Endearing You
A robot arrives in the mail, along with a letter. (tragedy)

239a9b85-10d8-4d54-8b76-9a679a1ec6d9.title: MPD Psycho
descriptionParagraphs: The main character is a detective, Kazuhiko Amamiya, suffering from Multiple Personality Disorder (a.k.a. Dissociative Identity Disorder). Starting out as a violent detective series with a twist (the twist being the variant personalities that take over Detective Amamiya at various intervals), the series evolves into an exceptionally complex and involved sci-fi conspiracy story.

f4cac440-3b9a-456b-b4ea-a387172e5c75.title: Hell Dogs
descriptionParagraphs: Can I kill a person as a police officer!? It's been three and a half years since I became a yakuza, and the infiltration never ends.
Kanetaka of the Higashi-Sheath Association is a gangster with a strong arm who has climbed up to assistant young head.
He landed in Okinawa at the command of the organization and killed his target, Kino.
That night, Kanetaka vomits violently.
He was an undercover investigator at the Metropolitan Police Department!
What is the purpose of Kanetaka's actions!?

00d21fb7-6a9c-487c-9427-b30ad2d3a29f.title: The Women Who Are Going To Hell
alternateTitles: Jigoku ni Ochiru Onna no Hanashi

descriptionParagraphs: From DH Publishing:

Mandala is the daughter of the King of Hell. Given two all-seeing crystal eyes, she is sent up into the world to save her dying clan from the invading western demons. However, she soon loses one of the crystals, and centuries later, her search is about to come to cataclysmic end.

alternateTitles: Aru Jigoku Eshi no Kokuhaku Jigokuhen
descriptionParagraphs: PANORAMA OF HELL is a shocking, tortuous journey into the depths of one man's postnuclear Hell. Through the confessions of a fiendish Hell painter born in the aftermath of the bombing of Hiroshima, Hideshi Hino tells a nightmarish story, creating a manga masterpiece of black humor, stunning vision, and unflinching imagery.

a223f16d-7a9d-411e-8246-71880819ef28.title: Tomino the Damned
descriptionParagraphs: Maruo's newest work, a story of twins being forced to join a travelling freak show.

a49db837-3ce9-4cba-9800-3b98f2d20760.title: Koisuru Jibaku-chan
alternateTitles: Suki na Hito no Mae de Jibaku suru Onnanoko

ca7556c4-f3d0-4b80-8c09-ec144cbd627f.title: Jigoku
descriptionParagraphs: A collection of twelve dreamlike stories by Nishioka Kyoudai.

3c87c7a3-611a-42ec-b395-756cda3b1f5f.title: Jitaku de Atlantis
descriptionParagraphs: An explorer's adventure in search of the ancient civilization of Atlantis inside a little girl's room.

4460d0d2-83d7-4cf5-beee-4d96f3f046a0.title: Kani ni Sasowarete
descriptionParagraphs: Collecting a handful of self-published shorts along with a mix of serialized stories and essays, panpanya's English-language debut mixes art styles and narratives from a range of genres.

If you are ever fortunate enough to see a crab strolling through your neighborhood, please follow its lead. By slowing down to a crab's pace and looking around and about in this world, you too may discover life's many mysteries that are hidden in plain sight.
Released in English by Denpa, LLC. in December 2018.

935c50ba-91ce-4fda-852a-a3755e7b5f05.title: Mechanical Marie
alternateTitles: My Robot Maid Can't Be This Adorable
descriptionParagraphs: Marie gets hired to be a maid. But not just any maid A robot maid!? How will she get through her new life pretending to be an emotionless mechanical maid? A manga full of comedy and romance!
Starts with a one-shot, and has been officially serialized in LaLa magazine.

53208ccd-66ee-4305-beda-e5db94fc26a3.title: Renai Jikaku Shoujou
descriptionParagraphs: 1-5) Renai Jikaku Shoujou

The beautiful, strong Agatsuma Tamaki has a weakness~ his kohai* (*junior in age or rank), Sawamura Kei, who simply just drives Tamaki up the wall by his mere existence. On one fateful night, Tamakis guilty secret was discovered by no other than! Will romance blossom between this wild but emotionally inept couple?
6) Kimi to Boku no Itsu Pobun

Horiuchi has always been precognitive and his cousin always gave him a hard time for that. Now his bully of a cousin has to stay with his family temporarily and his ribbing doesn't stop. Oneshot also found in

descriptionParagraphs: Love stories of the 10 princes of hell.

48910afe-3676-4a64-93c1-066b2cce4aa2.title: Bleach: The Unforgivens
descriptionParagraphs: One-shot story published as a special prologue chapter to the 4th Bleach movie, Jigoku-hen.

56219b48-3203-416d-9ea8-acf5352f55a3.title: Yuki wa Jigoku ni Ochiru no Ka
descriptionParagraphs: The "military history story concerning boys and girls" revolves around Yuki, a girl who has lived in the rural area of Kyoto with her five childhood friends who all share a secret that they cannot tell anyone. On her 16th birthday, Yuki's fate begins to change.

06c1b6d6-4134-464b-b64b-cad2c1b80386.title: A Story About My Girlfriend Whose Personality Changes Everyday
descriptionParagraphs: My girlfriend's personality changes everyday

89248e89-49cb-424b-899f-6c07f2289a96.title: Dr. STONE reboot: Byakuya
descriptionParagraphs: The last astronaut of humanity, Byakuya Ishigami, witnessed the moment when the entire planet was petrified. He was able to return to Earth later with five other members of the International Space Station, but how was he able to return to Japan?

a3d13cf9-7eb6-497c-b211-0638cf076929.title: Wakamono no Kuro Mahou Hanare ga Shinkoku desu ga, Shuushoku shite Mitara Taiguu Iishi, Shachou mo Tsukaima mo Kawaikute Saikou desu!
alternateTitles: Though young people recoil from entering the black magic industry, I found its treatment of employees quite good when I entered it, and the president and familiar are cute too so everything is awesome!
descriptionParagraphs: Franz is a recent graduate of magic school who is having trouble finding a job - he constantly bungles interviews due to his poor communication skills. With all the major magical jobs out of his reach, theres only one place left for him to go: the industry of black magic.

Known for being Disgusting, Dirty, and Dangerous, Franz is incredibly hesitant to actually enter such a market until he no longer has a choice. With his back to the wall, he talks to the Black Magic Incorporations CEO, who tells him the truth - black magic has shed its harmful exterior, and has instead become Pure, Pleasant, and Permissive. In short, Black Magic Inc. has actually become a white company.
Join Franz, his Cerberus boss, and his succubus familiar as they get into wacky adventures meeting other magicians, and getting to know them in the biblical sense.
By the author of "I've Been Killing Slimes for 300 Years and Maxed Out My Level" and "I, the Demon Lord, got married to the female hero's mother making her my stepdaughter."

98f43f70-07b2-4345-8db0-c3de0517ef36.title: The World of Moral Reversal (Fan Colored)
descriptionParagraphs: In our current society, most porn consumers are males, we are the ones who think with our d***** many times, we worship the female body and our society, products, advertisements and many other things are centered around that. But, what if it wasn't that way? What if, instead of men being the ones controlled by their sexual urges, women were the ones who bought porn magazines and had the most interest in sex? What if the moral standards between men and women were reversed?
A non-H adaptation of a doujinshi series with the same name.
